title: Big Year for Old School Wall Street Trades Gets Lost in AI Hype
description: Alongside all the triumphant AI talk, surging retail spirits and whiplash trades in crypto, a quieter trend was unfolding across global markets in 2025: diversified strategies posted some of their strongest returns in years.
